                            <comment id="12627031" author="ppoddar@apache.org" created="Fri, 29 Aug 2008 17:58:04 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;A relevant use case for multi-column versioning is setting version columns across primary and secondary tables. The version strategy and schema definition does not address the case where the columns are spread across multiple tables.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
